    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 996.2-generation Carrera, powered by the 3.6L M96 naturally aspirated flat-six. This powerplant utilizes VarioCam Plus for optimized valve timing and lift, delivering linear power through the 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut, featuring the signature rear-engine weight bias that provides exceptional traction under load. Essential preventative maintenance has been addressed, including an IMS bearing retrofit and a fresh rear main seal. The braking system remains sharp with four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is robust, exhibiting no signs of bore scoring and a clean DME report. This is a high-revving, analog machine ready for the apex.",
