      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been exceptionally well-cared for and stands in solid condition, ready for its next owner. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful use. All body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are free of significant curbing. Inside, the cabin is a clean, smoke-free environment; the seats show minimal wear, and the carpets have been protected by floor mats since day one. Every electronic feature, from the responsive infotainment screen to the heated seats and sunroof, operates perfectly. Mechanically, the car is sound. It starts up immediately, idles smoothly, and the transmission provides crisp, confident shifts. I have maintained a detailed log of all scheduled maintenance, including recent fluid changes and a brake inspection, ensuring the car drives as beautifully as it looks. This is a dependable, high-quality vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 32500.0,
